file.name: extension-in-flows-resolved.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: API
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /path:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A response.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object

components:
  securitySchemes:
    oauth2:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        authorizationCode:
          authorizationUrl: https://example.com/api/oauth/dialog
          tokenUrl: https://example.com/api/oauth/token
          scopes:
            write:pets: modify pets in your account
            read:pets: read your pets
        x-extension:
          prop: value
